data.title: Faisal II Irac Cyning
data.meta_description: Faisal II ricsode on Irac þǣm cynerīce of 4 Ēastermonaþ 1939 oðþæt þe man hine ofslog on 14 Mǣdmōnaþ 1958. He wæ Iraclandes endmesta cyning. He wæs be swicdōm ofsceat be his agnum heretoga in þǣm 14 Mǣdmōnaþ Onwendunge and mid him slogon ðā lǣwan manig on his cynne.
data.text: Faisal II (Arabisc: الملك فيصل الثاني Al-Malik Fayṣal Ath-thānī) ricsode on Irac þǣm cynerīce of 4 Ēastermonaþ 1939 oðþæt þe man hine ofslog on 14 Mǣdmōnaþ 1958. He wæ Iraclandes endmesta cyning. He wæs be swicdōm ofsceat be his agnum heretoga in þǣm 14 Mǣdmōnaþ Onwendunge and mid him slogon ðā lǣwan manig on his cynne.
